"The ID of the dashboard to embed. Available in the Superset embed dashboard "
"UI."
msgstr ""
"ID dari dasbor yang akan disematkan. Tersedia di antarmuka pengguna sematan "
"dasbor Superset."

#: xblock.py:64
msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Filter"

#: xblock.py:66
msgid ""
"List of SQL filters to apply to the\n"
"               dashboard. E.g: [\"org='edX'\", \"country in ('us', 'co')\"]\n"
"               The fields used here must be available on every dataset used by the dashboard.\n"
"               "
msgstr ""
"Daftar filter SQL yang akan diterapkan ke\n"
"               dasbor. Misalnya: [\"org='edX'\", \"country in ('us', 'co')\"]\n"
"               Field yang digunakan di sini harus tersedia pada setiap dataset yang digunakan oleh dasbor.\n"
"               "
